swProtocolVLANMIB.name: swProtocolVLANMIB
swProtocolVLANMIB.description: The Protocol (Policy-based) VLAN module MIB for the proprietary enterprise. Other related VLAN parameters will reference to rfc2674q.mib.

swProtocolVLANTable.name: swProtocolVLANTable
swProtocolVLANTable.description: A table that contains information about protocol (policy-based) VLAN method lists.

swProtocolVLANEntry.name: swProtocolVLANEntry
swProtocolVLANEntry.description: A list of the protocol (policy-based) VLAN methods.

swProtocolVLANIndex.name: swProtocolVLANIndex
swProtocolVLANIndex.description: A value that identifies this SwProtocolVLANEntry.

swProtocolVLANName.name: swProtocolVLANName
swProtocolVLANName.description: Specifies the name of the VLAN

swProtocolVLANProtocolType.name: swProtocolVLANProtocolType
swProtocolVLANProtocolType.description: The protocol type of protocol (policy-based) VLAN list. The group protocol types include dot1q-vlan(1), protocol-ip(2), protocol-ipx803dot3(3), protocol-ipx802dot2(4), protocol-ipxSnap(5), protocol-ipxEthernet2(6), protocol-appleTalk(7), protocol-decLat(8), protocol-dexOther(9), protocol-sna802dot2(10), protocol-snaEthernet2(11), protocol-netBios(12), protocol-xns(13), protocol-vines(14), protocol-ipV6(15), protocol-userDefined(16) and protocol-rarp(17)

swProtocolVLANAdvertisement.name: swProtocolVLANAdvertisement
swProtocolVLANAdvertisement.description: This object indicates whether advertisement is active or not.

swProtocolVLANUserDefinedProtocol.name: swProtocolVLANUserDefinedProtocol
swProtocolVLANUserDefinedProtocol.description: If the protocol type is protocol-userDefined(16), this value will fill with the user defined protocol type. This value will be ignored for other protocol types. The user cannot fill the pre-defined protocol type in this value. These pre-defined protocol types are: 0x0800 PROTO_VLAN_IPETHER2 0x8035 PROTO_VLAN_RARPETHER2 0xFFFF PROTO_VLAN_IPX802_3 0xE0E0 PROTO_VLAN_IPX802_2 0x8137 PROTO_VLAN_IPXSNAP 0x8137 PROTO_VLAN_IPXETHER2 0x809B PROTO_VLAN_APLTKETHER2SNAP 0x6000 PROTO_VLAN_DECETHER2 0x6009 PROTO_VLAN_DECOTHERETHER2 0x0404 PROTO_VLAN_SNA802_2 0x80D5 PROTO_VLAN_SNAETHER2 0xF0F0 PROTO_VLAN_NETBIOS 0x0600 PROTO_VLAN_XNSETHER2 0x0BAD PROTO_VLAN_VINESETHER2 0x86DD PROTO_VLAN_IPV6ETHER2

swProtocolVLANencap.name: swProtocolVLANencap
swProtocolVLANencap.description: If the protocol type is protocol-userDefined(16), this value will fill with the encap type. For other protocol types, this value will be ignored. The group encap type includes ethernet(1), llc(2), snap(3),and all(4).

swProtocolVLANRowStatus.name: swProtocolVLANRowStatus
swProtocolVLANRowStatus.description: This object indicates the status of this entry.

swdot1vProtocolPortTable.name: swdot1vProtocolPortTable
swdot1vProtocolPortTable.description: A table that contains VID sets used for Port-and-Protocol-based VLAN Classification.

swdot1vProtocolPortEntry.name: swdot1vProtocolPortEntry
swdot1vProtocolPortEntry.description: A VID set for a port.

swdot1vProtocolPortGroupPriority.name: swdot1vProtocolPortGroupPriority
swdot1vProtocolPortGroupPriority.description: The Priority associated with a group of protocols for each port.
